    "body": "This allows installing software on a namespace basis by including\r\n${NAMESPACE} in `install_path_scheme`. e.g.,\r\n\r\n```\r\ncat ~/.spack/config.yaml\r\nconfig:\r\n  install_path_scheme:\r\n      \"${ARCHITECTURE}/${NAMESPACE}/${COMPILERNAME}-${COMPILERVER}/${PACKAGE}-${VERSION}-${HASH}\"\r\n```",
